        Set.copyOf(Sets.difference(currProjects.keySet(), prevProjects.keySet())),
        Set.copyOf(Sets.difference(prevProjects.keySet(), currProjects.keySet()))
    );
}
```

This caches the projects maps and uses `containsKey` which is typically more direct than `hasProject` for Map-based implementations.

